  "the operating system is also responsible for file management. every document, image, video, and application is stored as a file. the os organizes these files into directories or folders and provides users with tools to create, delete, move, and modify them. without a file system, managing information on a computer would be nearly impossible.": "5fa53daa6c8c7dcf7061e2a2bb93e500",
